ğŸŒ GCS Static Website Bucket Module
ğŸš€ Welcome to the GCS Static Website Bucket Module!
This Terraform module provisions Google Cloud Storage buckets configured for static website hosting. It's designed to be reusable, composable, and flexible for your infrastructure needs.

ğŸ“– Overview
This module allows you to:
âœ… Create a Google Cloud Storage bucket.
âœ… Configure the bucket for static website hosting.
âœ… Set lifecycle rules, versioning, encryption, and retention policies.
âœ… Easily manage input variables and outputs.

ğŸ“‚ File Structure
â”œâ”€â”€ LICENSE         # License information (Apache 2.0)
